1. *Imao* je puno strpljenja. (He had a lot of patience.)
2. *Imala* je crvenu kosu. (She had red hair.)
3. *Imali* smo tu sreću. (We had that luck.)
4. On je *imao* dovoljno para. (He had enough money.)
5. *Imao* je sjajnu ideju. (He had a brilliant idea.)
6. Nismo *imali* vremena za odmor. (We didn't have time for a break.)
7. *Imala* je svoj stil. (She had her own style.)
8. *Imali* smo sjajnu večeru. (We had a great dinner.)